Cyclonus continued to kneel as he answered Unicron, "The matrix has
been stripped from its bearer and its power has been corrupted and used
to create new soldiers for your use mighty lord."

At that moment a door irised open and Deepstryke, Phobia, Nightrazor,
Decibel and Tumult stepped through and after a glance at Cyclonus also
knelt down facing Unicron. Scourge also stepped up and knelt down.

Cyclonus resumed his narrative. "Rodimus Prime has lost the power of
the matrix and has either passed into oblivion or has reverted to his
lesser form. In any case he is no threat to us."

Preston
